Reality TV star Khloé Kardashian told ex Tristan Thompson that she might need to “borrow” some sperm if they want to give their daughter a sibling.
During the episode Kardashian had called Thompson to talk about what to do with True’s old toys.
“What happens if we have another girl?” Thompson asked Kardashian.
